        <p style="text-align: justify;"> This is to confirm that {!Booking__c.S__c} {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c} aged about {!age} years, S/o. Mr. {!Booking__c.Son_Daughter_Wife_of1__c} have purchased  {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} measuring 117.00 square meters, in the land called. Zuari Garden City – Plots  {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} on  the Project Land measuring 40630.438 Sq meters –falling under survey Nos. 5/1, 105, 107/1, 107/2, 107/3, 107/4, 111/2, 111/1A, 111/1B, 121 &amp; 123 etc., - situated at Hulikere Village, Belagola Hobli, Sriranagapatna Taluk, Mandya District, Karnataka,  for a total consideration of<B> Rs. {!Booking__c.Quote__r.Total_Sales_Consideration__c} /-( {!amountInWords})</B> We confirm that we have obtained necessary permissions/approvals/sanctions for construction of the said land from all the concerned competent authorities and the development of the said Plots as well as of the  {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} is in accordance with approved plans.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">We assure that the development  {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} the land appurtenant thereto is not subject to any encumbrance, charge or liability of any kind whatsoever and that the entire property is free and marketable. We have a clear, legal and marketable title to the said property and every part thereof..</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">We have no objection to your giving a loan to the above buyer/s and his/her/their mortgaging the said {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} to your Bank by way of security for repayment, not with standing anything to the contrary contained in the Sale Agreement dated<B> &nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd'-'MM'-'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!Booking__c.Agreement_Executed_Date__c}"/></apex:outputText> </B>entered into between us and {!Booking__c.S__c} {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c}</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">We also undertake to inform and give proper notice to the co-operative housing society as and when formed, about the {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} being so mortgaged.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">We hereby undertake to forward the original title deed as and when the same is executed and duly registered directly to  {!Booking__c.Loan_Bank_Name__c} Ltd. {!Booking__c.Loan_Bank_Address__c} without parting the same with the purchaser of the {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} during the pendency of the loan. It is agreed by us that until execution of the necessary sale deed we shall retain the possession of the {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} for and on behalf of {!Booking__c.Loan_Bank_Name__c} Ltd. We undertake that we shall execute the sale deed/transfer deed in favour of {!Booking__c.S__c} {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c} on or before &nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd'-'MM'-'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!Booking__c.Refund_Expected_Date__c}"/></apex:outputText></p>
