        <p style="text-align: justify;">We agree that in the event {!Booking__c.S__c} {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c}, being the Borrower/s of your Bank defaults in making the payment of the EMI for {!emiMonths} months, your Bank if required shall have the right to substitute the purchaser in its sole discretion after payment of transfer charges (if any) to us.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">We agree and undertake that, in case of cancellation of the allotment of the above {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name} for whatsoever reason, we shall deduct Rs. {!Booking__c.Cancellation_Charge__c}/- of the total consideration and /or as provided in the agreement and refund to you, directly, the balance amount to the extent financed by you. The remaining balance amount will be refunded to the Purchaser/s. </p>
